  <brief_title>The Effect of Carotid IMT (Intima Media Thickness) on Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Patients Undergoing Off-Pump Coronary Artery Bypass Graft Surgery</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
